'''''N''-甲基-D-天門冬胺酸受體'''（{{lang-en|'''N-methyl-D-aspartate''' '''receptor'''}}，簡稱'''NMDA受體'''或'''NMDAR'''）為[[麩胺酸鹽|麩胺酸鹽]]受體，是一個主要的分子裝置，控制[[突觸|突觸]]的可塑性與記憶功能<ref name="pmid19605837">{{cite journal | author = Li F, Tsien JZ | title = Memory and the NMDA receptors | journal = N. Engl. J. Med. | volume = 361 | issue = 3 | pages = 302–3 | year = 2009 | pmid = 19605837 | pmc = 3703758 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMcibr0902052 }}</ref>。

NMDA受體是一種離子型麩胺酸鹽受體的特別型態。[[NMDA|NMDA]]（'''N'''-甲基-D-天門冬胺酸）是一種選擇性致效劑，可以與NMDA受體結合，但是無法和其他麩胺酸鹽受體結合。NMDA受體的結合，會導致[[離子通道|離子通道]]非選擇性地開啟，使陽離子通過，進而使[[平衡電位|平衡電位]]改變至接近0毫伏特。NMDA受體進行活化，必須依賴電壓，這會導致離子通道會阻擋細胞外的Mg<sup>2+</sup>與Zn<sup>2+</sup>離子通過，並允許Na<sup>+</sup>離子與少量Ca<sup>2+</sup>離子流入細胞，以及使K<sup>+</sup>離子流出細胞，並保持電壓的依賴性<ref name="pmid10049997">{{cite journal | author = Dingledine R, Borges K, Bowie D, Traynelis SF | title = The glutamate receptor ion channels | journal = Pharmacol. Rev. | volume = 51 | issue = 1 | pages = 7–61 | date = March 1999 | pmid = 10049997 | doi =  | url = http://pharmrev.aspetjournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=10049997 | access-date = 2014-04-27 | archive-date = 2020-10-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201027013532/https://pharmrev.aspetjournals.org/content/51/1/7.long }}</ref><ref name="pmid11775847">{{cite journal | author = Liu Y, Zhang J | title = Recent development in NMDA receptors | journal = Chin. Med. J. | volume = 113 | issue = 10 | pages = 948–56 | date = October 2000 | pmid = 11775847 | doi =  | url = http://www.cmj.org/Periodical/LinkIn.asp?journal=Chinese%20Medical%20Journal&linkintype=pubmed&year=2000&vol=113&issue=10&beginpage=948 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140427010101/http://www.cmj.org/Periodical/LinkIn.asp?journal=Chinese+Medical+Journal&linkintype=pubmed&year=2000&vol=113&issue=10&beginpage=948 | archivedate = 2014-04-27 | access-date = 2014-04-27 }}</ref><ref name="pmid11399431">{{cite journal | author = Cull-Candy S, Brickley S, Farrant M | title = NMDA receptor subunits: diversity, development and disease | journal = Curr. Opin. Neurobiol. | volume = 11 | issue = 3 | pages = 327–35 | date = June 2001 | pmid = 11399431 | doi = 10.1016/S0959-4388(00)00215-4 | url = http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0959-4388(00)00215-4 | access-date = 2014-04-27 | archive-date = 2020-07-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200724052137/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0959-4388%2800%2900215-4 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="pmid17088105">{{cite journal | author = Paoletti P, Neyton J | title = NMDA receptor subunits: function and pharmacology | journal = Curr Opin Pharmacol | volume = 7 | issue = 1 | pages = 39–47 |date=February 2007 | pmid = 17088105 | doi = 10.1016/j.coph.2006.08.011 | url = }}</ref>。

